name: Usual.Art
tagline: some sounds and pictures for use in real digital life
body:
### Usual.Art for use.
it is a linux oriented sound-themes mainly for gnome+kde for this moment

https://github.com/Symbiants/usual.art

tarballs:

https://github.com/SyMbiANtS/usual.art/blob/master/echoe.synth.1.tar.bz2
https://github.com/SyMbiANtS/usual.art/blob/master/mageia.guitar.6.tar.bz2
https://github.com/SyMbiANtS/usual.art/blob/master/mageia.light.synth.1.tar.bz2


noarch rpm can be obtained here:

    http://abf-downloads.rosalinux.ru/symbiants_personal/repository/rosa2012.1/x86_64/main/release/

and spec file for rpm is in:
